Package edu.monash.fit2099.game.actors

This module is about the actors that can exist in this edu.monash.fit2099.game.

This module explores the different actors within the edu.monash.fit2099.game and how they function and interact with one another. Note that all actors in this package extend the abstract actor class in engine code.

Since:
1.0.0
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Enemy
    Abstract class that represents an Enemy to the Actor
    Goomba
    A little fungus guy.
    Koopa
    Class that represents a Koopa (like a turtle), who is an enemy to the player.
    Player
    Class representing the Player.
    Toad
    A global Singleton class representing the Toad.
